\sum\limits^{^N}_{i=1} \frac{(1-x)}{w}^{i-1}.
\sum_{i=1}^N \frac{(1-x)^{i-1}}{w} = \frac{1}{w} \sum_{i=1}^{N} (1- x)^{i-1} = \frac{1}{w}\cdot \frac{1\cdot (1 - (1 -x)^N)}{1 - (1 - x)} = \frac{1}{w}\cdot\frac{1 - (1 - x)^N}{x}
